      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（休日。雫宛の荷物が届いたので、部屋を訪ねた）",
      "startTime": 6.366666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4566.666666666667,
          "startTime": 10.933333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　鍵は開いてるな\n雫、入るぞ？　入るからな？　お邪魔しまーす……",
      "startTime": 15.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3999.999999999998,
          "startTime": 19.266666666666666
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5966.666666666667,
          "startTime": 21.233333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん",
      "startTime": 24.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……不法侵入？",
      "startTime": 26.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや……違うんだ\n一応ノックはしたんだけど、返事がなかったから……",
      "startTime": 30.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "DVD、観てただけ……\nヘッドホンしてたから、気付かなかった……",
      "startTime": 35.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……雫宛の宅配便、持って来たんだ",
      "startTime": 40,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう……ございます",
      "startTime": 44.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "……中身……見た？",
      "startTime": 46.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "見てない見てない。そんなことしないって",
      "startTime": 49,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、中身はアイドルのブルーレイ\nライブの……",
      "startTime": 56.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "結局自分で言うのか……\n見て欲しいのか欲しくないのか、どっちなんだ……",
      "startTime": 59.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "……部屋、入られちゃったし……\n隠さなくても、いいかなって……",
      "startTime": 66.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それは……すまない。それにしても\n意外とアイドルグッズを飾ってないんだな",
      "startTime": 74.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "……そう？",
      "startTime": 77.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは\nどんな部屋を……想像していたんですか？",
      "startTime": 80.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルが大好きって言うから\nもっとアイドルグッズで一杯なのかと思ってたよ",
      "startTime": 85.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "ファンにも、スタンスはいろいろ\nでも……私は、違うので",
      "startTime": 92.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "グッズ集めて、グループを応援する人……\nアイドル文化を、楽しむ人……",
      "startTime": 99.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "私は……後者なので\nグッズより、文化に興味がある",
      "startTime": 104.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル文化……尊い……",
      "startTime": 107.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "文化、か……\nなんだかスケールの大きな話だな",
      "startTime": 113.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと、ない……日本のアイドル文化\nたかだか、六十年とちょっと。意外と歴史、浅い……",
      "startTime": 120.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　それって浅いのか？\nっていうか、やっぱり詳しいんだな……",
      "startTime": 129.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "勉強したので……当然のこと\nちなみに、日本のアイドル文化……すごく独特",
      "startTime": 136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "昔から、アイドルのほとんどが\n未熟な十代を指していたから……",
      "startTime": 143.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "海外のアーティストが、完成されたパフォーマンスを\nファンに見せるのとは、根本的に違う……",
      "startTime": 150.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル個人がどんな過程を経て、どんな風に\n成長するのかを見守る……それが日本のアイドル文化",
      "startTime": 158.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそんな文化が根付いたのか……国民性？\nそのルーツもまた、アイドル文化の中にあるはず……",
      "startTime": 169.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_szkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "szkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_01-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、{user}さん？",
      "startTime": 174.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
